<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.2">
<l>uruki neñcē niṉaintiṅ kirunteṉ toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>muruku vaṇṭuṇ malarkkai taiyiṉnī ḻalilmuṉorunāḷ</l>
<l>peruku kātaṉ maiyeṉṉuḷ ḷameytap pirintāṉiṭam</l>
<l>porutu munnīrk karaikkē maṇiyun tupullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sitting here languishing, thinking [of him], [my] heart, what [is it for]?</l>
<l rend="indent">Arise; we will worship</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi, where the battling three waters [of the sea] cast jewels to the shore,</l>
<l>The place of the one who, one day previously, departed</l>
<l rend="indent">when welling passion arose in my heart</l>
<l>In the shade of the screw pine [tree] with blossoms that honeybees sip.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
